<br>
In the past, I was in a guild who only used the 'can and will' highest roller method and that has always worked for me. Another officer has suggested a points method. It seems to be the same type of points method Wraith uses. We plan to have 30-40 active members 40+ so lewt issues are bound to pop up.<br>
<br>
I am curious what your thoughts on lewt rules are? The positives sides and negative sides of both and what other options and ideas there may be. Since this is such a high volume board, I figured it would be a great start.<br>
<br>
Lae<br>
<br>
