<center><font face=’veranda’ color=#7d1b7e> Tree Hugger of the 53rd Season </font></center><center><span style='filter:glow(color=#e54c2c,strength=3);width:100%'><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=441293 target="_blank">Saccro Tomato</a></span></center>
<center><font face=’veranda’ color=#f75431> Befriender of the 41st Stick in the back</font></center><center><font face=’veranda’ color=#f52887 size='0'><a href=http://www.eqfaces.com/cgi/files/engine/profile.php?personalID=1271 target="_blank">I’m Real</a></font></center><br><center><font face=’veranda’ color=#c35817><a href=http://www.guildportal.com/Guild.asp?GuildID=3163&TabID=22176>Officer of Protectors of Nightfall</a>
